Ok. So there are two different Andy Williams Christmas DVDs on Amazon. My mom loves Andy Williams so we have both. This is the difference.
If he has WHITE sweater on the cover, it is the disc from PBS,  where it is all the old footage from his Christmas specials.
If he has a YELLOW sweater on the cover, it is clips from his old show, and his live Branson Christmas show from the late 80s/early 90s.

Great DVD. Classic and nostalgia, memories. He died same day my father died, September 26 2012. So more personable to Me. Watched his shows in 1960s when growing up. Seller was fast and honest and would use seller again and others should use seller too. Thanks.

We thoroughly enjoyed this dvd.  Unlike some other reviews, we thought the sound and quality of this dvd was very well done.  I would definitely recommend getting this one; I'm certainly glad I got it for my husband for Christmas.  The music was so very well done and brought back a lot of great memories of the Andy Williams Christmas shows back in the day when they were so popular.
